    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for someone looking for a major project or a source for parts. Mechanically, the engine requires significant repair and currently struggles to stay running, while the transmission shifts roughly. The exterior has substantial rust spots, fading paint, and several large dents, and the interior shows heavy wear including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. It will likely need to be towed and requires a full mechanical overhaul to be roadworthy again.",
